cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.HC 

The paper proposes a method for ensemble classifier aggregation, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The application of the proposed method is in a brain-computer interface, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural engineering (cs.NE). The classification task involves visually evoked potential, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the application is in a brain-computer interface, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
